    <string name="about_app"><![CDATA[
        Pengyou is an open-source app that helps you learn Chinese.
        Open-source means that you can get involved to improve the app! Just head over to the
        project\'s <a href="https://github.com/Mr-Pepe/pengyou">Github page</a> and start submitting
        bug reports and feature requests or contribute code yourself. <br/><br/>

        Pengyou heavily depends on open-source projects that make data like stroke orders
        and the dictionary itself accessible to everybody. For a full list of used data sources
        have a look <a href="https://github.com/Mr-Pepe/pengyou_data_generator">here</a>. <br/><br/>

        The stroke order diagrams make use of the <a href="https://hanziwriter.org/">HanziWriter
        </a> project. <br/><br/>

        Evelyn Li did an awesome job designing the app icon and user interface. Check out <a
        href="https://www.instagram.com/evelyncplum/">her Instagram page</a> to see more of her
        work.
    ]]></string>
